# Website env vars live in the repo root — do not duplicate keys here.
#
# 1. Copy the root template:  cp .env.example .env.local  (from repo root)
# 2. Fill in values in root .env.local
# 3. Install direnv and run:  direnv allow  (at repo root and in apps/website)
#
# The website inherits root vars via apps/website/.envrc (source_up → root .envrc → .env.local).
# See README.md → Environment setup.
